			h2 style="margin-top:0" About Dan
			p I am a data journalist, programmer, and photographer. I'm currently Head of Data at #{link_to "Skift", "//skift.com"}, where I lead both application development and 
				data research. Previously, I was a #{link_to "news application developer at ProPublica", "http://www.propublica.org/site/author/dan_nguyen"} and a reporter at the #{link_to "Sacramento Bee", "//sacbee.com"}. 
