				self-published a series of 
			  #{link_to "popular", "http://photography.bastardsbook.com/"}  
				#{link_to "online books", "http://ruby.bastardsbook.com/"}.
			

			h4 Technical notes
			p I built this portfolio site using the #{link_to "Middleman framework", "//middlemanapp.com"}, a static site generator in Ruby. 
				So it's just plain HTML, CSS, and JS files #{link_to "hosted on Amazon's S3 service", "http://www.smalldatajournalism.com/projects/one-offs/using-amazon-s3/"}, 
				which makes it easy to maintain and fast to load. 

